    autocmd!    CursorMovedI   swoopBuf   :call   s:cursorMoved()

    autocmd!    BufWrite    swoopBuf    :call   SwoopSave()
    autocmd!    BufWinLeave   swoopBuf   :call  SwoopQuit()
augroup END
